Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, NenDo!-kun and friends\Nvisit a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These clouds are white.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are grey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Let's paint them better colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use a paint brush!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use an ink brush!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a roller!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}NenDo!-kun and friends create\Nlarge brushes and a roller
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and climb a staircase towards the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Up they go, one step at a time,\Nuntil they reach the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has the paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought {\i1}you{\i0} brought it, NenDo!.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun knows just how to paint the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}NenDo!-kun and friends too are\Ndyed in a crimson red.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rain, rain, go away!

